Subject: nos aieux nous montrent le chemin-our ancestors show us the way
------------------------------------------------------------
   Chers amis de la conference Le Francais,
   Dear friends from conference Speakers Corner,

   Vous voudrez bien trouver en commentaire a ce message
   Please find attached as a comment to this message
une authentique lettre de la femme-ecrivain Francaise
a genuine letter from French woman-writer
George SAND a son celebre amant Alfred de MUSSET.
George SAND sent to her famous lover Alfred de MUSSET.

   Si vous savez lire entre les lignes, peut-etre y decouvrirez
   If you know how to read between lines, maybe you will find
vous un second sens plus profond.
a deeper second meaning in it.

              X
              X

PS: La forme de ce premier message devrait vous aider.
PS: The display of this first message should help you.


